    <title>Reference Implementation of Tinkar</title>
    <para>This section shall include user documentation for a reference implementation of the
        Terminology Knowledge Base standard, referred to as Komet ( insert hyperlink ), and how
        various terminologies, such as SNOMED, LOINC, RxNorm, and HL7 terminologies shall be
        reproducibly represented using the Terminology Knowledge Base standard.  Using the Komet browser we can view the search concepts, view the concept details, and navigate hierarchies among many other functions that are outside the scope of this ballot.</para>
  <section>
      <title>Concept Detail</title>
      <para>Below we see the details for the LOINC concept Homocystine [Mass/time] in 24 hour Urine.
            You can see the LOINC ID, data from the LOINC table, Solor assigned Names, and
            relationships from the LOINC - SNOMED CT Cooperation Project.</para>
